items.name: The Anima Stone
explicitMods: +1 to maximum number of Summoned Golems
+1 to maximum number of Summoned Golems if you have 3 Primordial Items Socketed or Equipped
items.descrText: Place into an allocated Jewel Socket on the Passive Skill Tree. Right click to remove from the Socket.
flavourText: All revere the earth they walk,
For it wields strength beyond compare,
Stands long after all else falls.

items.name: Tempered Spirit
explicitMods: -1 Dexterity per 1 Dexterity on Allocated Passives in Radius
2% increased Movement Speed per 10 Dexterity on Allocated Passives in Radius
items.descrText: Place into an allocated Jewel Socket on the Passive Skill Tree. Right click to remove from the Socket.
flavourText: Though the body rots, the spirit lives on.
<default>{This item can be transformed on the Altar of Sacrifice along with Vial of Transcendence}

items.name: Watcher's Eye
explicitMods: 30% increased Maximum total Energy Shield Recovery per second from Leech while affected by Zealotry
12% increased Movement Speed while affected by Grace
items.descrText: Place into an allocated Jewel Socket on the Passive Skill Tree. Right click to remove from the Socket.
flavourText: One by one, they stood their ground against a creature
they had no hope of understanding, let alone defeating,
and one by one, they became a part of it.
